- What are all the controllers that are are enabled by default in Controller manager component?
Kubernetes default controller are the replication controller, endpoints controller, namespace controller, and serviceaccounts controller - https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/command-line-tools-reference/kube-controller-manager/
